    Are you afraid to smile? Embarrassed about your teeth? Or maybe you just want a better looking smile. Recapturing the beauty of your smile is easier than you think. Dental veneers, the primary smile enhancement, is used in extreme makeovers and can dramatically improve the appearance of your teeth.

Dental veneers are wafer-thin, custom-made shells of tooth-colored materials designed to cover the front surface of teeth to improve your appearance. These shells are bonded to the front of the teeth changing their color, shape, size or length.
